itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"成班文盲,講paulinho 做咩撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「如果熱刺陣中有誰會離隊（轉戰中超），我會覺得非常驚訝，<span style=\"color: red;\">這事應該未來兩季也不會發生</span>。因為我們正準備迎接一些非常好的事，如果他們選擇不參與其中真是十分不智。」卡尼最後道。"},{"pid":"5b4b2a97e854f720ad4a32c29700eae1a378469d","tid":84882,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國無未來</span></span>"}]}